      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-yellow-50 border-[3px] border-amber-300 p-6 md:p-8 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">The $150/Hour Consultant With No Website</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider font-black">Why "I'm too busy" is losing you money</p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            My friend James charges $150/hour for IT consulting. Fully booked. Makes great money.
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Problem:</strong> No website. Gets all clients through referrals.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-amber-100 border-l-[4px] border-amber-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-amber-900 font-medium">
              <strong>What happens when referrals slow down?</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-amber-900 mt-2">
              One month. That's all it took. His main client put projects on hold. Suddenly he had 3 billable hours/week instead of 30.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We built a site in Durable. 30 seconds. Added case studies from his past work. Connected Calendly for bookings.
          </p>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Three months later?</strong> He's fully booked again. But now 40% of leads come from organic search.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-green-100 border-l-[4px] border-green-500 p-4 my-4">
            <p class="text-sm text-green-900 font-medium">
              <strong>The lesson:</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-green-900 mt-2">
              Your website is your safety net.<br><br>
              Referrals are great - until they aren't.<br><br>
              Durable takes 30 seconds. That's not too much time to invest in your business's safety.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            But James later upgraded to Framer. Why? Because he wanted to charge $250/hour.<br><br>
            Premium rates require a premium site. Durable looks "good enough" for $150/hour. Framer looks "worth $250/hour."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOOL COMPARISONS -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Top 3 Builders for Consultants</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {tools.map((tool, index) => (
          <div class={`border-[3px] p-6 ${index === 0 ? 'border-[#F5521A] bg-[#FFF8F0]' : 'border-gray-300 bg-white'}`}>
            {tool.badge && (
              <span class={`inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 ${
                index === 0 ? 'bg-[#F5521A] text-white' : 'bg-gray-900 text-white'
              }`}>
                {tool.badge}
              </span>
            )}
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900">{tool.name}</h3>
              <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#F5521A]">{tool.rating}</div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-4">{tool.verdict}</p>

            <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase">Pros</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                {tool.pros.map(pro => (
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                    <span>{pro}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-2 mb-6">
              <p class="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase">Cons</p>
              <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
                {tool.cons.map(con => (
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-red-600 mt-0.5">✗</span>
                    <span>{con}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>

            <a href={`/reviews/${tool.name.toLowerCase().replace(' ', '-').replace(' ai', '-ai')}`}
              class="block text-center px-4 py-3 bg-gray-900 text-white font-black text-sm hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">
              Read Review
            </a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURE COMPARISON -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">
